/* Age estimation */ The Royal College of Paediatrics and Child Health (RCPCH) has described dental x-rays to determine the age of asylum seekers as "imprecise" and "inappropriate". According to Tim Cole, Professor of medical statistics at the Great Ormond Street Institute of Child Health, dental x-ray tests are "very inaccurate" in determining a precise age.
